setWaypointStatements 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: The waypoint is done only when the condition is fulfilled. When the waypoint 
 is done, the statement expression is executed. 
Within the Condition &amp; Statement code string: this refers to the group 
 leader thislist refers to an array containing each unit in the group 
 
Syntax:  
 waypoint setWaypointStatements [condition, statement] 
Parameters: 
waypoint: Array - format Waypoint 
[condition, statement]: Array 
condition: String 
statement: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing